metadata.Plot: Not quite ready to open its gates to the public, the endangered-species-oriented Eden Wildlife Zoo receives a group of college students who apply for a zoology internship. But, an ill monkey will soon lead to virulent contamination, as the deadly disease that starts to infect the animals one by one, is turning them into ravenous undead predators. Now, it's up to Dr Ellen Rogers and her skeleton crew to fight the virus and the zoo's zombified inhabitants before they escape. Are humans next in the long list of endangered species?
metadata.Actors: Ione Butler, Andrew Asper, LaLa Nestor
